hopobject.body: What do you study? accommodation-med.com Marie-Philip Poulin and Meghan Agosta-Marciano will without a doubt figure prominently into the offensive game plan, as they are in current form arguably the Canadians’ best forwards. Spooner, Rebecca Johnston, and Haley Irwin will also be counted on to put up points. Brianne Jenner and Jenn Wakefield both had very impressive showings in Ottawa in April, and also likely slot in on the top three lines, though Wakefield’s versatility will probably factor into the kind of role she plays.
